---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Silk Screen Printing in Armenia | Bulk T-Shirt & Uniform Printing Yerevan"
  description="Professional silk screen printing in Yerevan, Armenia. Ideal for bulk orders, corporate uniforms, and durable branded apparel."
>
  <main>

    <h1>Silk Screen Printing in Armenia (Yerevan)</h1>

    <p>
      Silk screen printing is the most cost-effective solution for bulk textile production.
      It is widely used for uniforms, corporate branding, and promotional clothing.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>What is Silk Screen Printing?</h2>
    <p>
      Ink is pressed through a stencil (mesh screen) onto fabric.
      This method is ideal for high-volume orders with simple or limited-color designs.
    </p>

    <h2>Best For</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Corporate uniforms</li>
      <li>Event T-shirts</li>
      <li>Promotional clothing</li>
      <li>Bulk apparel orders</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Order Types</h2>

    <h3>Bulk Orders</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Low cost per unit</li>
      <li>Ideal for 20+ pieces</li>
      <li>Consistent print quality</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Business Clients</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Staff uniforms</li>
      <li>Brand merchandise</li>
      <li>Event apparel</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advantages</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Very low cost for large quantities</li>
      <li>Extremely durable prints</li>
      <li>Best for simple logo designs</li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <h2>Order Silk Screen Printing</h2>
    <p>
      Send your design, quantity, and garment type. We will calculate pricing and production time.
    </p>

    <a href="/en/quote">Request a Quote</a>

  </main>
</Layout>